    <item>
      <title>随着影响力的增长，马来西亚将任命国王为警察部队“荣誉”负责人</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-21/malaysia-king-set-to-extend-powers-as-honorary-police-chief</link>
      <description><![CDATA[马来西亚政府准备任命易卜拉欣·伊斯坎达尔国王为警察部队的“荣誉”负责人，这一新职位可能会让国王扩大在这个东南亚国家的权力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-21/malaysia-king-set-to-extend-powers-as-honorary-police-chief</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Mar 2024 02:18:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着法律费用的增加，特朗普在竞选筹款方面落后于拜登</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-21/trump-trails-biden-on-campaign-fundraising-as-legal-fees-mount</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普的政治运作在 2 月份额外花费了 560 万美元的法律费用，削弱了这位共和党推定提名人的政治筹款活动，而该筹款活动继续落后于他的民主党对手的现金筹集。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-21/trump-trails-biden-on-campaign-fundraising-as-legal-fees-mount</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Mar 2024 02:07:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>“政治地震”震撼了越南的继承斗争</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-21/-political-earthquake-shakes-up-succession-battle-in-vietnam</link>
      <description><![CDATA[越南可能没有出现许多民主国家分裂的两极分化的选举，但在短短一年多的时间里第二位总统的下台表明，一党制国家内部的闭门权力斗争也可能同样残酷。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-21/-political-earthquake-shakes-up-succession-battle-in-vietnam</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Mar 2024 01:52:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>在印度印地语中心地带，农民的困境并没有阻碍莫迪</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/features/2024-03-21/farmers-in-rural-india-hold-key-to-modi-winning-third-term-as-prime-minister</link>
      <description><![CDATA[执政的印度人民党日益根深蒂固的受欢迎程度在很大程度上依赖于农村地区——但许多人只看到该党执政十年来所带来的好处有限。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/features/2024-03-21/farmers-in-rural-india-hold-key-to-modi-winning-third-term-as-prime-minister</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Mar 2024 01:00:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>葡萄牙中右翼领导人在选举中以微弱优势获胜后被任命为总理</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-21/portugal-s-center-right-leader-named-prime-minister-after-narrow-election-win</link>
      <description><![CDATA[葡萄牙中右翼领导人路易斯·黑山在其联盟本月以微弱优势赢得选举后被任命为总理，这给他带来了试图以少数派政府执政的挑战。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-21/portugal-s-center-right-leader-named-prime-minister-after-narrow-election-win</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Mar 2024 00:26:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>斯里兰卡将于下周开始债券重组谈判</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-20/sri-lanka-to-start-restructuring-talks-with-investors-next-week</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，全球投资者和斯里兰卡官员预计下周将开始谈判，旨在重组价值 120 亿美元的全球违约债券。该国的美元债券上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-20/sri-lanka-to-start-restructuring-talks-with-investors-next-week</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 20 Mar 2024 20:03:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>委内瑞拉下令逮捕马查多的竞选经理和高级助手</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-20/venezuela-orders-arrest-of-machado-s-campaign-manager-top-aides</link>
      <description><![CDATA[委内瑞拉政府周三下令逮捕反对派领导人玛丽亚·科里纳·马查多的九名高级助手，因为他们涉嫌参与破坏尼古拉斯·马杜罗政府稳定的阴谋。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-20/venezuela-orders-arrest-of-machado-s-campaign-manager-top-aides</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 20 Mar 2024 19:20:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国海军舰艇在海上争端中尾随菲律宾海岸警卫队</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-20/philippines-says-chinese-navy-ship-seen-circling-amid-sea-spat</link>
      <description><![CDATA[菲律宾表示，一艘中国海军舰艇在前往菲律宾占领的南海岛屿的途中“尾随”其海岸警卫队船只，这是两国声称存在重叠海洋主张的最新事件。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-20/philippines-says-chinese-navy-ship-seen-circling-amid-sea-spat</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 20 Mar 2024 11:16:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>越南国家主席辞职，领导层出现新的动荡迹象</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-20/vietnam-s-president-quits-in-latest-sign-of-leadership-turmoil</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据越南共产党的一份声明，越南国家主席武文上于周三辞职，成为在对该国一些最高领导层调查范围扩大之际最新辞职的高级官员。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-20/vietnam-s-president-quits-in-latest-sign-of-leadership-turmoil</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 20 Mar 2024 10:12:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
